{"tid":751061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺現時啲家長思想真係好歪曲 點教好下一代？","createTime":"2018-07-21T13:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T14:01:39.000Z","uid":20241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e1f70846157f2cbe2ff074791ecca7fa49ff1f56","tid":751061,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:40:30.000Z","msg":"頭先同啲家族親戚聚餐<br />\n席間例牌講佢地啲仔女點點點啦<br />\n詳情就唔多講<br />\n但發現佢地有個一致認同既思想<br />\n<br />\n只要個樣野搵到錢 話知佢傷天又害理 只要唔犯法就支持下一代做 覺得你醒目仔大把前途<br />\n<br />\n但如果下一代做緊個樣野冇辦法即刻搵到 話知你做緊既野可以救到個世界又好 或者成功左搵到錢又好 呢一刻搵唔到食你就係地底泥係垃圾家族恥辱<br />\n<br />\n如果一個地方既大部分人由細都係呢種氛圍之下成長 咁你話幾咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be5f4200d2bcf4da31d0fa552919e65abf606bf","tid":751061,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:41:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6bc7fb56e6a886727e6889bcc8f13fbe09215e6","tid":751061,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:44:51.000Z","msg":"即場問佢個女幾錢q"},{"pid":"3540738443028c917e9ade65eb9852b6a25f5989","tid":751061,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T13:51:29.000Z","msg":"Sex work is work <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf93cf9f1a4e5b53cd29caf708b4bbee9c17bd7","tid":751061,"uid":19932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T14:01:39.000Z","msg":"唔當場出聲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}